&lt;li&gt;Featured timelines in a carousel on the home page&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improved Create Timeline experience (see above)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Several bug fixes in response to users’ comments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description><link>http://globurg.tumblr.com/post/53517844959</link><guid>http://globurg.tumblr.com/post/53517844959</guid><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2013 10:35:55 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>Editing your timeline is easy! And you can edit it at any time....</title><description>&lt;img src="http://24.media.tumblr.com/19d664bac0f760025941d41d883542a8/tumblr_mojv2ifET01svgtoio1_500.png"/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;p&gt;Editing your timeline is easy! And you can edit it at any time. Just click the “edit” button and Glomento will show you all the posts that are available within your chosen timeframe.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can check the posts you want to appear, and uncheck the ones you want to leave out. You can also increase or decrease the time window to show more or fewer posts. And you can change the title if you want to!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When you’ve made your changes, just click “done” to see your timeline.&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>http://globurg.tumblr.com/post/53210319743</link><guid>http://globurg.tumblr.com/post/53210319743</guid><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2013 14:23:06 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>Release 2 is out now!
We now have a second release ready for...</title><description>&lt;img src="http://31.media.tumblr.com/1c54099121ac4d8fed51f9fa13ec1900/tumblr_moe9c8njeH1svgtoio1_500.png"/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Release 2 is out now!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We now have a second release ready for Glomento. We’ve packed a lot of user suggestions into this release. Some changes you will notice:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong id="docs-internal-guid-365fb39d-43ca-3b49-8294-1b5596dd1852"&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;No hashtagging necessary! Glomento grabs all the photos and checkins available. You can just do what you do naturally, and use glomento later to craft your timeline.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Sign in with Instagram! Users told us they prefer Instagram to Twitter, so we switched it.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Edit your timeline. Include the best photos and leave out the rest, to better reflect what you want to represent your memory.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Grow or shrink your timeline. You can now define a timeline as taking place over several days, or restrict it to just a few hours, so you have more control.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Users voiced a lot of concerns about privacy, so we’ve added the ability to keep a timeline private.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;A profile page for every user so you have all your stuff in one place.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Featured timelines on the home page so you can see timelines that other users have created.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You’ll notice a lot of other little cosmetic changes too, like maps being included with foursquare checkins and timelines displayed in a mosaic-like block instead of a long scrolling line.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
